        <item>
            <title>【评测】PS5 Pro / PlayStation 5 Pro 详细效能评测，实机游戏 60fps 画面 + 新光追效果放大睇 + 打机温度噪音</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/ps5-pro-review/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/ps5-pro-review/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273358</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>PS5 Pro (PlayStation 5 Pro) 将于 11 月 7 日正式发售，新机引入更强处理晶片，带来更强处理能力之余，能够保持细小的机身，确是非常吸引！但好多人都有疑惑，新机售价去到 $5,780，明显是专门给对游戏画质、流畅度有追求的玩家而设，究竟是否适合自己去购买呢。而这些画质、流畅度的变化，实际又是如何呢？今次我们就在发售之前，同大家介绍一下转用 PS5 Pro 后获得的各方面提升，给大家在选购之前作一个参考。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03524-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>自 PS5 推出以来，玩家都要在画质与流畅度之间做出选择。在 4K 解像度上想获得更清晰、更多细节表现的画面，无可避免牺牲游戏流畅度；相反如用游戏中的「效能模式」，虽然保持到 60 或接近 60fps 的流畅度，但游戏清晰度就有明显下降。PS5 Pro 就能给玩家既用到游戏的高画质模式，又同时能够达到如 60fps 的流畅度。</p><p>PS5 Pro 采用更强劲的 GPU，比 PS5 在光线追踪（Ray Tracing）的处理速度快了 2-3 倍，并引入全新 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 升级解像技术，带来更精致的画面和流畅的游戏体验。我们将通过几款热门游戏的实测结果，来看看 PS5 Pro 是否值得你考虑入手。</p><h2>外观与设计</h2><p>首先我们来看看 PS5 Pro 的外观特点，在之前的开箱文章也有介绍过，如果你已看过那篇文，可跳到下面游戏评测部份。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1-489x580.jpg" alt="" width="489" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1-489x580.jpg 489w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-1.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 489px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-1.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 的高度与 PS5 基本相同，但机身阔度缩小至与 PS5 Slim 一致。重量相比起 PS5 Slim 的 2.58kg，PS5 Pro 只增至 3.06 kg，如果同最初版本 PS5 的 4.48kg 比较的话，PS5 Pro 就显得十分轻盈了，适合大家四处移动或搬到朋友家打机。对比初被 PS5，PS5 Pro 整体体积却有所缩小，虽然高度、厚度未必会有好大分别，但机身阔度上就窄了很多。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03567.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲同 PS5 Slim 一样，如果同初代 PS5 比较，机身阔度窄了很多</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲上图左方 PS5 Pro, 右方初代 PS5</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 背面 USB 的排列与 PS5 Slim 版相似，同样提供 2 个 10Gbps 传输速度的 USB Type-A 插口、LAN 与 HDMI 插口。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03550.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>如 PS5 Slim 版一样机身表面提供两个 USB-C 接口，其中一个支援连接 SSD 时获得 10Gbps 速度，另一个则可连接无线耳机或手掣的转插头，或者有线游戏装置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-1.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>散热设计延续了 PS5 的风格，机顶部分无散热孔，减少积尘风险，但黑色外壳容易留下指纹。值得注意的是，PS5 Slim 的光碟机可与 PS5 Pro 共用，但另购的外壳无法兼容。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273623" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03576.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273625" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03598.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>▲同 PS5 Pro Slim 一样，主机灯光延续了 PS5 一</p><p>不过就我们所见，PS5 Pro 中央的位置都几易积尘，特别是它黑色的表面，用家最好勤于打扫。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4075-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>散热与噪音表现</h2><p>我们测试了初代 PS5 和 PS5 Pro 在玩《霍格华兹的传承》30 分钟后的温度。结果显示两者的散热表现非常相似，PS5 Pro 的机背温度为 41.2℃，而 PS5 为 42.1℃，差异不大。只是用家较易接触到的机顶，PS5 Pro 会较为凉快（PS5 Pro:21.4℃, PS5: 23℃)。噪音方面，我们在底噪 40.7 分贝的房间内进行测试，开机 30 分钟之后 PS5 Pro 的机顶噪音为 42.7 分贝，机背为 45.9 分贝，而初代 PS5 机顶的 43.4 分贝以及 44.8 分贝。就同 Slim 版一样，Pro 版构造令面向玩家一方的机顶会稍微安静，反而玩家轻难听到的机背噪音较大，结果就是玩家实际听到的噪音较小。尤其是在一米的游戏距离下，基本听不到风扇声音，夜晚的游戏体验不会被噪音打扰。</p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"></td><td valign="top">PS5 Pro</td><td valign="top">PS5</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">机顶噪音</td><td valign="top">42.7dB</td><td valign="top">43.4dB</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">机背噪音</td><td valign="top">45.9dB</td><td valign="top">44.8dB</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">机顶温度</td><td valign="top">21.4℃</td><td valign="top">23℃</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">机背温度</td><td valign="top">41.2℃</td><td valign="top">42.1℃</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">机面温度（下半部）</td><td valign="top">29.7℃</td><td valign="top">26.7℃</td></tr></tbody></table><p>机顶噪音：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03619.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲PS5 Pro: 42.7dB</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03628.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲PS5: 43.4dB</p><p>机背噪音：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462574662_1223749832.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro: 45.9dB</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03629.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5: 44.8dB</p><p>机顶温度：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462555496_1081753186.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro: 21.4℃</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462583258_1518197262.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5: 23℃</p><br /><b><ul><li>保真 <b>Pro </b>模式：此模式针对喜欢体验新光追图像效果的玩家，包括反射和阴影的增强。玩家可在画质上探索全新的光影效果，城市景观的细节和密度都显著提高。</li><li>性能 <b>Pro </b>模式：针对 60 FPS 进行提升，透过 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) 技术保留高画质，同时启用光线追踪，并支援水面与窗户内部的反射效果，提供流畅且画质优秀的体验。</li></ul></li><li>光线追踪增强：新增环境遮蔽与关键光影计算的光线追踪，特别在远距离景物中表现出色，为场景添加更为逼真的阴影和光线反射，提升了游戏的沉浸感。</li></ul><figure id="attachment_1273361" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1273361" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110594117-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="ht