li>改进的材质和光影效果：PS5 Pro 增强了赛道与周边物件的反光处理，包括挡板、金属物件和灯光，实现更精细的环境光影效果，尤其在赛车行驶时的湿地反射令人印象深刻。</li></ul><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110625217-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110625217-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110625217-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110625217-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
