            <title>YouTube Premium 跨区「印度人」新解约潮，之前都无事但今日大量网友中招</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/youtube-premium-5/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=youtube-premium-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/06/youtube-premium-5/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:58:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[youtube premium]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273518</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube 疑似再次收紧 Premium 会籍费用政策，若使用土耳其、印度版本的 YouTube Premium，YouTube 已出电邮通知用户要使用印度境内的付款方式。有网民在社交平台上发文，指自己今日开始已用不到  YouTube Premium。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273519 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289-438x580.jpg" alt="" width="438" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289-438x580.jpg 438w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/462537122_8674094289.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 438px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲若使用印度版本的 YouTube Premium，12 月 5 日前需将付款方式更新为印度境内付款方式</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">YouTube 向用户发送电邮，指「印度的 YouTube Premium 会籍费用须使用印度境内的付款方式支付。」若想保留会藉，必须在 2024 年 12 月 5 日前将付款方式更新为印度境内的付款方式。网民在 LIHKG 表示「收到 email 要一个月内 update 做印度信用卡」。有网民回复指不只印度，好多土耳其用户亦收到通知要更改付款资料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273555 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241106_3_01_592.jpg 963w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-694x544.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-694x544.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1.jpg 1149w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网民在 LIHKG 表示「收到 email 要一个月内 update 做印度信用卡」（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x169.png" alt="" width="694" height="169" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x169.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1280x311.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_.png 1292w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲网民笑指「打紧杖呀点去银行出卡」（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">其他网民就表示不如直接使用 AD Block，亦有网民建议直接使用香港版本 YouTube Premium，并取笑「封得你迟啦」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273521 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_.jpg 756w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲其他网民就表示不如直接使用 AD Block（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273527 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1-694x180.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="180" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1-694x180.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241106_-1-1.jpg 1218w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民取笑「封得你迟啦」（图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>）</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3815057/page/3">LIHKG</a>、Youtube</p><br /><b>
]]>
